    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Ticket to collect and discuss remaining work for the Cython 3.3 release.\n\n- How far are we from a release?\n- Is anything left open that should be included?\n\nMain features so far:\n- Pattern matching\n- Generics / subscripted container types\n- `@cython.collection_type()`\n- `restrict`\n- more speed\n- more thread safety\n- smaller modules, more shared code\n- remove Py3.8 support, keep Py3.9+\n\nLink to release milestone:\nhttps://github.com/cython/cython/milestone/118",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
