            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I don't think there's too much from me. It seems as good a time as an to release something.\n\nJust looking at recent stuff, https://github.com/cython/cython/pull/7713 might be worthwhile (but also should be basically user-invisible).\nI'd have liked to get the free-threading limited API in, but is almost certainly a much bigger chunk than we want to do for this release and there isn't much benefit of having only some of it (although not much harm either) so I think we should defer that.",
